{"tid":2073030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解有人搞反國安法街站 無人搞全港反國安法簽名活動","createTime":"2020-06-21T04:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T05:16:56.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"123bff552843c93c34c8dcac14574cc39fe76a64","tid":2073030,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"人地網上又好 街上又好<br />\n日日都有數字同Post 出街<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地數字靚 畫面靚 俾晒數字同對白政府拎出嚟講</span></span></strong><br />\n我地宜家唔可以遊行用人數表達⋯<br />\n<br />\n點解連網上既數字都唔俾國外朋友睇！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果每個區議員都搞一個簽名活動<br />\n我相信一樣加埋都有幾十萬人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n網上搞 可以全世界好多人都會反對！<br />\n<br />\n如果黑警到時搞事 <br />\n亦可以拎返佢地保護支持國安淺街站既相去對比！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解無人做！"},{"pid":"782a0b4bf3beec894635f5d0217bcce3b6a0691a","tid":2073030,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"因為無人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1a7ec2be5a2359cf525d7ba7ac0e26b7f64016","tid":2073030,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"因為一定少過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93533fe8a19302948f750d96fb9afeef4032eed1","tid":2073030,"uid":25582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:45:25.000Z","msg":"因為會比人斬囉"},{"pid":"e652354c69b82623d762ff1169958b3c86efabfc","tid":2073030,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:45:30.000Z","msg":"你覺得做呢啲共產黨就會驚？"},{"pid":"0aa8417642afcf918cc2da54b4bed0ad73dcc3bb","tid":2073030,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"咪有囉<br />\n係咪得你個區無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94802b05b4aac71a5695b9deae3030